moduleMetadataJson.name: Architecture Migrate
moduleMetadataJson.description:
This module checks if the meterpreter architecture is the same as the OS architecture and if it's incompatible it spawns a
                          new process with the correct architecture and migrates into that process.
author: Koen Riepe (koen.riepe <Koen Riepe (koen.riepe@fox-it.com)>

options.name: WORKSPACE
options.description: Specify the workspace for this module

options.name: SESSION
options.description: The session to run this module on.

options.name: EXE
options.description: The executable to start and migrate into

options.name: FALLBACK
options.description: If the selected migration executable does not exist fallback to a sysnative file

options.name: IGNORE_SYSTEM
options.description: Migrate even if you have SYSTEM privileges
